test_name: Treatment affecting biomarkers aligns across visits
short_desc: If TRTBIOMARK[prev_vis]= 1, then TRTBIOMARK should not equal 0
full_desc: If Q1. TRTBIOMARK (treatment affecting biomarkers) = 1 (Yes) at previous visit, then Q1. TRTBIOMARK (treatment affecting biomarkers) should not equal 0 (No)

short_desc: If ADVEVENT[prev_vis] = 1, then ADVEVENT should not equal 0
